{"tid":1560861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男「出差偷情」時猝死　法院判工傷：公司需付高額賠償金","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:55:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26967f099c5993002045218d69ec6112300f2fb0","tid":1560861,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"法國1名已婚男子因公出差，但他在旅程中和剛認識的女子發生性關係，激情過後還因心臟病發而不幸過世。法院認為員工出差時有性行為是正常的，判定男子是工傷死亡，他的公司除了要付賠償金給男子家屬，連原本該付的養老金也得一併支付。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，法國巴黎(Paris)的鐵路建築公司TSO聘用工程師沙維爾(Xavier X)在2013年時到盧瓦雷省(Loiret)出差。男子到了當地之後，約了1名女性到自己下榻的酒店發生性行為，事後被人發現陳屍在房內，經法醫驗屍後確認他是因心臟病發而身亡。<br />\n<br />\nTSO公司認為沙維爾心臟病發當時，並不是在履行職務，並指責沙維爾「和陌生人發生通姦行為」；法院則認為，員工在出差期間應獲得雇主的保障，無論是在履行職務的當下或其他時間內，「性行為是正常生活中的活動，就像洗澡或吃飯一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n沙維爾過世被認定是工傷，TSO公司需支付原工資約8成的金額給他的家屬，時限是直到他原本的退休年齡。除此之外，TSO公司到時還得繼續支付養老金。"},{"pid":"144bc2be7e8b28b297ee37fd058e6ede0665ef8b","tid":1560861,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"dde782cea9945f81c8cb32b83fafb6c1951d55a8","tid":1560861,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5efd45d46dc0bc8117dfe6487820a07a7dd0ea2d","tid":1560861,"uid":52793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"法院認為員工出差時有性行為是正常的<br />\n<br />\n一定係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d634ee3e51a93a18ed8d90c2b34d9b6d302242c0","tid":1560861,"uid":317880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"如果企係佢老婆角度睇，咁判又好似無咩問題。"},{"pid":"c1a79201630d2d3a0d0dc743db255370752f88c8","tid":1560861,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"法國唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06de65f1b03190e9a26a8df0058401c837e575e1","tid":1560861,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"堅㗎喎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/employer-held-liable-for-workers-death-after-sex-9nflwtptg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Femployer-held-liable-for-workers-death-after-sex-9nflwtptg&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=b75b1016\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/employer-held-liable-for-workers-death-after-sex-9nflwtptg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過緊要時刻唔好推無聊post<br />\n多謝手足分享<br />\n請善用不推文回覆</span></span>"}]}